msg.msgText: The name must not have leading or trailing spaces and cannot contain control characters, comma, double quote, backslash or equals sign. The first character must not be a number or any of the following special characters: ! # $ '' ( ) * + , - . / : ; = ? @ % or single or double quote mark, less than or greater than sign, and ampersand sign.

msgExplanation.p: The name does not meet the restriction.

msgUserResponse.p:
Ensure that the name does not contain the listed special characters or leading or trailing spaces,
and that the first character is not a number.
